<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">هـ ي ف:</span> <span class="c2">(الْهَيَفُ)</span> بِفَتْحَتَيْنِ ضُمْرُ الْبَطْنِ وَالْخَاصِرَةِ، وَرَجُلٌ <span class="c2">(أَهْيَفُ)</span> وَامْرَأَةٌ <span class="c2">(هَيْفَاءُ)</span> وَقَوْمٌ <span class="c2">(هِيفٌ)</span> . وَفَرَسٌ <span class="c2">(هَيْفَاءُ)</span> ضَامِرَةٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>